<!doctype html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>페이지 없음</title>
    <style>
      body {
        display: grid;
        min-height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
        place-items: center;
        background: #080908;
        color: #f5f6f4;
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      }
      main {
        width: min(100% - 32px, 480px);
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1 {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 28px;
      }
      p {
        margin: 0 0 24px;
        color: #9aa09a;
      }
      a {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 42px;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #fee500;
        color: #191600;
        padding: 0 16px;
        font-weight: 900;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <h1>페이지를 찾을 수 없습니다</h1>
      <p>요청한 페이지는 공개되어 있지 않습니다.</p>
      <a href="./">계산기로 돌아가기</a>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
